# simple_json_api
Simple JSON API using gin framework

Build and run the binary
```
go build
./simple_json_api --PORT=5000 --MODE=release
```
`--PORT` specifies the port to run on
`--MODE` specifies the Webserver run mode 


Example cUrl 
````
curl --location --request POST '0.0.0.0:5000/v1/ticket' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
